s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想瘦加多件風嬲</blockquote><br />\n咁撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你跑10k咪3x分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099df2c65f580fa37b891eb177ddb79a66435363","tid":89630,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似講過減磅最好係跑耐而唔係快<br />\n利申聽返黎</blockquote><br />\n唔樣減埋肌肉&mdash;》降低BMR&mdash;》唔改善飲食&mdash;》體重反彈指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係快好過耐？我都係聽過耐會燒埋肌肉所以一直快跑</blockquote><br />\n我以前係淨係跑步，最後反彈。之後改左做gym+跑步，好左好多</blockquote><br />\n有去玩下泰拳"},{"pid":"2ed48a6c9b8cc7d1c47f5ccfa89dc928168b9975","tid":89630,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實空肚會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係？怕唔怕會燒肌肉<br />\n雖然我想減脂但唔想以減肌為代價"},{"pid":"2b88d50ce0f727582dfb179420d9d0d1d94fee90","tid":89630,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c671a4547326d5731f4b6967b81a7a52cebc0fa","tid":89630,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"我想問埋空肚跑怕唔怕減埋肌肉啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6b8581f0fa0a2958b2492d415a5d8ea670827e","tid":89630,"uid":76221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問埋空肚跑怕唔怕減埋肌肉啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我估會，你諗下，你跑步既energy來自肝醣。當你空肚跑，加上肚餓，身體進入飢荒狀態，首先將消耗較多能量既肌肉轉化做能量，然後先轉化脂肪。當你再食野，身體首先把食物轉做脂肪作儲存，以備再次飢荒。所以又越減越肥。"},{"pid":"468643784e50b8b6a8feec69e731c234c5255859","tid":89630,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:55:43.000Z","msg":"乜肌肉會小架咩"},{"pid":"85389dbed523dbe085e53084f806110c4f889eea","tid":89630,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"咁我想問埋，快跑係咪會冇咁易減埋肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814dc65ee5bf88eecce33625e3c0f7e50c933079","tid":89630,"uid":62668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"跟6號一樣行青山道/彌敦道?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e76e73cfa08524da545328f378c25a102db14b1","tid":89630,"uid":76221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁我想問埋，快跑係咪會冇咁易減埋肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實而家好流行HIIT 或tabata，佢地都有跑步既訓練。跟著跑會易減D同冇咁晒時間。當然，飲食先係最重要，7分靠飲食，3分靠運動。"},{"pid":"078dbed411a20751e15b384a3061c1278765f4a3","tid":89630,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟6號一樣行青山道/彌敦道?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇跑青山道, 但係跑彌敦道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba0b54288fc7e2e215542524244198103e3bd33","tid":89630,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T13:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁我想問埋，快跑係咪會冇咁易減埋肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實而家好流行HIIT 或tabata，佢地都有跑步既訓練。跟著跑會易減D同冇咁晒時間。當然，飲食先係最重要，7分靠飲食，3分靠運動。</blockquote><br />\n如果跑步既, 即係類似快慢交替跑?"},{"pid":"8ec8ee0207cfbc58fc433f497c6f330528b813f8","tid":89630,"uid":26686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T13:26:39.000Z","msg":"你一跑過20分鐘多數係減肌減脂<br />\n多數大隻fit果啲人都係跑8分鐘為修身線條<br />\n<br />\nching 減肥運動唔係重點 <br />\n飲食習慣先係重點 <br />\n仲有 空肚跑 如果你冇碳水係身會用蛋白質黎燃燒<br />\n到時就即係話你小左蛋白質幫你build肌肉<br />\n最好先搞習慣 例如脂肪率高既野唔好食"},{"pid":"cc391fe0aec6641093be2b3ab2f53aa71d3d